      "span_text": "Three-dimensional radiation transport models were required to adequately represent neutron streaming through volumes of gas in the complicated Magnox geometries; these were developed using the UK Monte Carlo neutron transport code MCBEND [CITATION_1] and were also used to to underwrite the predictions of the models by validation against the measurements (Sect. 3.1)."
